									I created <a href="https://github.com/openstf/stf" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline font-semibold">OpenSTF</a>, 
									a device lab management tool that grew to <strong class="text-white">13,000+ GitHub stars</strong>. 
									Success, right?
								</p>
								
