									<strong class="text-yellow-400">The burnout was real.</strong> Hundreds of open issues, no time to address them, 
									users frustrated, maintainer exhausted. Sound familiar?
								</p>
								
								<p>
									Then <strong class="text-blue-400">AI happened.</strong> Claude Code can write quality code from GitHub Actions. 
									But tokens aren't free, and someone still needs to review. 
