										</svg>
										<span class="text-xl font-bold">openstf/stf</span>
									</div>
									<a href="https://github.com/openstf/stf" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition">
										View on GitHub ‚Üí
									</a>
								</div>
								
								<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
									<div class="text-center">
										<div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text mb-1">13.8k</div>
										<div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">GitHub Stars</div>
